---

import { Separator } from '@/components/ui/separator'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="mb-12 sm:mb-20 min-h-screen container">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">About Me</h1>
    <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-7 sm:leading-9">
      Hi there, I'm Kishan. I'm a product engineer who likes taking fuzzy
      ideas all the way to shipped products. My work sits around AI agents,
      evaluation systems, developer tools, native apps, and full-stack products
      that need to feel fast, reliable, and useful.
      <br />
      <br />
      These days, I work at Plivo as a Software Engineer II, building
      infrastructure around AI agents. I work on agentic workflows, simulation
      and evaluation systems, debugging tools, model fine-tuning, and
      reliability features that help teams improve agents before they touch
      production traffic, including the voice-agent workflows I work on at
      Plivo.
      <br />
      <br />
      Outside work, I build products like Suniye, a privacy-first native macOS
      dictation app, and GitaGPT, an AI advisor that reached 13M+ views and
      120K+ users. I enjoy building the whole thing: product, frontend, backend,
      infra, and the small details that make something feel finished.<br
      />
      <br />Previously, I worked at Quinence, where I built and led full-stack
      products across recruiting, training, automation, CMS workflows, and Web3
      commerce, including systems that handled 2,200+ transactions and around
      $369K in sales. <br />
      <br />If you’re interested in collaborating or have a project in mind,
      feel free to reach out to me at{' '}
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@kishans.in?cc=kishansharma1231@gmail.com&subject=Hey%20Kishan%2C%20we%20have%20some%20exciting%20opportunity%20for%20you"
        class="text-black underline"
      >
        hello@kishans.in.
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 sm:mt-10 mb-4 sm:mb-5"
    >
      Experience
    </h2>
    <ul class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <div
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-xs bg-gray-900 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-mono text-xl font-semibold"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          P
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">Plivo</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
            Software Engineer II
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">Nov 2024 → Present</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />
      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/quinence.png"
          alt="Quinence logo"
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-xs"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">Quinence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
            Software Engineer
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">June 2022 → Nov 2024</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />
      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/increff.png"
          alt="Increff logo"
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-xs"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">Increff</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
            Software Developer (UI) Intern
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">January 2022 → May 2022</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />

      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/ncr.png"
          alt="NCR Technologies logo"
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-xs"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">NCR Technologies</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
            Software Developer Intern
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">May 2021 → Aug 2021</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />

      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/digimall.png"
          alt="Digimall logo"
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-xs"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">Digimall</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
            Software Developer Intern
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">March 2021 → May 2021</p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
